                06:00 PM TO 11:00 PM</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h5 class="s-title">Amenities</h5>
        <div class="s-amenities">
          <div class="amenity"><img src="../assets/images/wifi.svg" alt=""><span>Free Wifi</span>
          </div>
          <div class="amenity"><img src="../assets/images/noun_parking area_1585952.svg" alt=""><span>Parking</span>
          </div>
          <div class="amenity"><img src="../assets/images/noun_Teddy Bear_922207.svg" alt=""><span>Kids Play Area</span>
          </div>
          <div class="amenity"><img src="../assets/images/noun_Bar_1919977.svg" alt=""><span>Alcohol Available</span>
          </div>
